realm.name: author
realm.description: can only see their own books, except for sales count, and add content

realm.name: editor
realm.description: can create books, modify and delete their books, and read other editors' books but not do anything on them

realm.name: director
realm.description: can access about everything, except they can see books but not modify anything

clientScopes.name: roles
clientScopes.description: OpenID Connect scope for add user roles to the access token
